node.content: Delivery and self pick-up not available
Islandwide Delivery, Minimum Spending of S$ 11
HEYTEA Singapore. The original cheezo tea 2012, fostering joy & inspiration with every sip.

Iced 650ml or hot 500ml heytea's original since 2020. juicy seasonal fresh harumi tangerine hand peeled daily steeped in refreshing regal aqua green tea, with smooth osmanthus pudding & crunchy bobo pops to deliver an inspirational, zesty taste experience.

The ultimate refreshing expression of our very mango grapefruit. Fresh seasonal mango, hand cut & prepared daily. Blended with refreshing regal aqua green jasmine tea with additional ruby grapefruit pulp & crunchy konnyaku bobo pops for that additional textured mouthfeel. A true concoction of taste & texture that is so poppingly refreshing.
Fresh seasonally selected juicy mango with refreshing regal aqua green jasmine tea delivering a sweet tropical taste experience. Available in 500ml standard & 650ml upsized.
A sip of grapefruit delight fresh pulpy blend infused with jasmine tea will make you never want to go back to any other & does not include cheezo topping.

An inspirational, indulgent blend of our popular strawberry cheezo & peach cheezo. A harmony of the fruity sweetness from strawberries & peach juice, further amped up by the refreshing floral regal aqua green jasmine tea. Comes in the standard 500ml size available for upsize to 650ml.

A healthy flavourful drink born of a perfect union of EMBLIC SUPERFRUIT and DEYTEA's signature AQUA GREEN. This drink promises a refreshing sweet taste experience with a tinge of sourness. Here at HEYTEA, we call it 7 part sweet 3 part sour.
HEYTEA ORIGINAL 2018. Fresh handpeeled Kyoho Grapes blended with premium Aqua Green tea.
HEYTEA's original since 2016. A sip of grapefruit delight - selected fresh pulpy blend infused with Aqua Green jasmine tea will make you never want to go back to any other.
Your new go-to refreshment this summer. Crafted with mango chuncks, marsh grapefruit pulp and coconut milk, blended with our premium Aqua Green tea, while bobo pops brings extra fun.
HEYTEA's original since 2017. Blend seasonally selected juicy mango with vibrant Aqua Green tea, the drink is refreshing ad dense with sweet tropical temptations.
Roasted Brown BoBo Milk with Cheezo (Original)
HEYTEA's original since 2012. A combo of Brown Sugar Bobo with fresh milk topped with classic cheezo, presenting you rich and mellow mouthfeel, a fulfilling experience.
A lite version of the Roasted Brown Bobo Milk (Original). featuring a delightful combination of Brown Sugar Bobo and Premium fresh milk; delivering a rich velvety taste experience.
Roasted Brown Bobo Milk Tea With Cheezo

Premium Red Blossom black tea, mixed with creamy and rich milk. A taste-bud-tingling blend with floral aroma lingering in your mouth. Extra sweetness added with chewy Brown Bobo at the bottom and Classic Cheezo atop.
A TARO inspiration, complete with taro paste (orh nee) and taro bobo. A pure taro delight.
Pure Aqua Green Jasmine Milk Tea
A harmonious blend of refreshing Regal Aqua Green Jasmine tea with real premium fresh milk, atop a layer of tender smooth osmanthus pudding.
The original cheezo tea since 2012. A unique blend of fresh tea leaves sourced from all over the world for a brisk and clean flavor. Topped with Cheezo.
Pure Regal Aqua Green Jasmine Tea
Brewed with premium green tea, it tastes brisk and clear with a hit of Jasmine aroma.
Fresh, crisp tea is swirled into hyper-rich milk ice cream, then topped with a handful of sweet , gooey Brown Sugar Bobo.
Lucent Crystal Pudding made from Natural rock sugar, mildly sweet with a soft crunchy texture.
Bouncy and chewy experience inspired by Bobo Pops.
Chewy experience inspired by gooey Taro Bobo.
Steamed and handmade daily using natural taro; to deliver a rich and smooth taro taste experience.
Osmanthus Oolong Pudding is tender and smooth in texture. Present you refreshing and rich floral smell.
Inspirational toppings with full-bodied fresh grapefruit pulp.
HEYTEA ORIGINAL & classical Cheezo made of whipped cream.
Cool experience inspired by creamy and milky flavor.
